item.title: Butterfly Trunk
item.description:
Your Funny Uncle posted a photo:

I've never seen so many butteflies together in my life. Actually, I don't think I've seen a thousandth as many butterflies together in my life! They were all over the trees, with some flying about between. One even landed on my arm, but I couldn't get a shot of it as i had my telephoto lens on my camera at the time.

item.title: First Sighting
item.description:
Your Funny Uncle posted a photo:

After reaching the reserve we then had to climb on foot for another 50 minutes or so (no mean feat at altitudes approaching 3000m.) All of a sudden we started to come across butterflies.
